# Measat VSAT Broadband Management

The Measat VSAT Broadband Management is a custom connector built for Measat to monitor custom parameters on an NMS. Custom Parameters include the Overall Site Count, Congestion of the networks, Traffic and Capacity Monitoring and Rain Analysis.

## About

